00:04:25.780 --> 00:04:27.440
Ergenliğin simgesi!  

00:04:27.440 --> 00:04:29.110
Gençliğin baharı!  

00:04:29.110 --> 00:04:31.360
<i>Tres-tres-tres bien!</i>  

