00:06:24.280 --> 00:06:25.480
O zaman...  

00:06:43.150 --> 00:06:45.400
Sence bozulmuş mudur?  

00:06:45.400 --> 00:06:46.690
<i>Non</i>...  

00:06:50.610 --> 00:06:52.940
Ben alırım.  

00:06:53.900 --> 00:06:55.190
